channel.title: Start of apprehension.
channel.description:
At the start of apprehension after you drop down to the trams there is an area where you can get stuck in the map and cannot get out.
It is a gap off the side of one of the trams sorry no picture of it but there is a map problem in the area at the bottom with all the trams.
